                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Phelps</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-05-15"><hi rend="italic">May 15,
                                1893</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Samoan affairs, dispatch 561, England and Germany will prolong until
                            March 31 next, if we agree.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Phelps.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
